3FB935C1.Line5.1000C2: Thank you, stranger. You should stick around, meet the boss. We could use more people like you in Backwater.

8EB1E23D.Line1.1000C2: I knew it. You're done, Tomaj. Pack your bags.

B76D18CD.VoiceDir3.101BAB: Disbelieving; panicked. His fate has just been sealed.

DEE80E0A.VoiceDir1.1000C2: Smug, self-righteous; her suspicions have been confirmed.
